{"tid":1334610,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"工聯會荃灣活動中心(疑)檢出炸彈","createTime":"2019-07-20T07:23:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-20T07:43:54.000Z","uid":238013,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"5a63795b642a47f9b4e479e561aaf15448f26280","tid":1334610,"uid":238013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T07:23:41.000Z","msg":"【搗破武器庫●不斷更新】警撿爆炸品拘一人 Ｏ記：數個月前開始跟進  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【15:05】現場對開德士古道來回全線已解封<br />\n 【15:00】爆炸品處理課人員陸續將餘下的爆炸品引爆 <br />\n【14:45】現場對開德士古道來回全線封閉，料即將再度引爆 <br />\n【13:30】O記表示，數個月前開始接手跟進案件 <br />\n【13:20】警方表示，警方當場拘捕一名27歲男子，不排除有更多人被捕<br />\n 【13:20】警方表示，在單位內撿獲大量製作炸藥的材料，撿獲10枚已製成的燃燒彈、TATP炸藥，當中軍火專家已引爆1KG的TATP炸藥 <br />\n【13:15】警方展示撿獲的證物，包括多個頭盔及眼罩、大聲公、丫叉、手套<br />\n 【12:50】警方將會進行封路措施，預料德士古道來回全線封閉 <br />\n【12:40】警方證實以涉嫌無牌管有爆炸品拘捕一名男子 <br />\n【12:35】隆盛工廠大廈及鄰近兩座大廈的市民正在疏散離開現場，警方拉起封鎖線防止有人接近大廈 <br />\n【12:30】消防員到場戒備，並帶同消防喉前往隆盛工廠大廈 <br />\n【12:10】警方正準備疏散隆盛工廠大廈鄰近兩座大廈的市民，稍後準備於隆盛工廠20樓後樓梯進行二度引爆 <br />\n【11:55】警方稍後會於大廈20樓走廊或梯間將懷疑爆炸品引爆<br />\n 【10:15】據悉警方拘捕一名涉案男子 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190720/59842784\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190720%2F59842784&d=JxnBaozbJlL%2F%2BfT%2BMtMvbvrL6OgrijQqmkkA1x3Ej7w%3D&h=a8803f62\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190720%2F59842784&h=f5779677\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190720/59842784</a>"},{"pid":"ad58bd00346503a78b2aa0841e63ff09917607be","tid":1334610,"uid":80560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T07:24:01.000Z","msg":"又來自編自導自演"},{"pid":"291213fb17313732fbf0bec8441a56f078e92f35","tid":1334610,"uid":143343,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T07:24:32.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">工聯會</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cf756aecc5c781cf5711c041fc649c33df5dac8","tid":1334610,"uid":156791,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T07:25:04.000Z","msg":"O記表示，數個月前開始接手跟進案件 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a2c1b2a80463dec73587538e41db89966eabff1","tid":1334610,"uid":90515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T07:25:31.000Z","msg":"工聯會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n叫麥美娟出黎解釋下！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86c6a4696d11f1bc6fbc924796e7c6e123616da9","tid":1334610,"uid":54921,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T07:25:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74ffdba6f2246f378eeaffbd14779565cd60c8ed","tid":1334610,"uid":199727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T07:26:21.000Z","msg":"丫叉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n穿左煲啦<br />\n係想郁你就唔會用丫叉啦<br />\nBBQ咩"},{"pid":"3248fda51755c0080c8efd5687a3f2714a60372a","tid":1334610,"uid":214192,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T07:28:41.000Z","msg":"原來個活動中心係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">工聯會</span></span>嘅，咁搜到都唔出奇啫，畢竟係佢哋<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">專長</span></span>嚟"},{"pid":"2353fc25d0bafd192ae7e4c123da393cab754346","tid":1334610,"uid":2617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T07:32:10.000Z","msg":"成篇文邊到有工聯會"},{"pid":"e7b680c100d6fa4a630594fc6f66ef4d749569c5","tid":1334610,"uid":21501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T07:33:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5931727571e211a710f02de4ceb51e4fe3c57235","tid":1334610,"uid":2031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T07:41:46.000Z","msg":"【15:35】<span style=\"color: red;\">香港民族陣綫</span>承認今日於荃灣工廠大廈被捕的男子為該組織成員，現時已經有律師協助保釋，又指該倉庫一直僅作為存放音響及其他宣傳物資之用，<span style=\"color: red;\">未知為何會有爆炸品存放在該單位</span>。"},{"pid":"950f49c42f199bfe0708bd9a0dfad84891adc4ab","tid":1334610,"uid":53254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T07:43:54.000Z","msg":"工聯, 割了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}